item.title: CVE-2017-20018|2024-08-05T21:45:24.555Z -- unspecified -- xampp
item.description: A vulnerability was found in XAMPP 7.1.1-0-VC14. It has been classified as problematic. Affected is an unknown function of the component Installer. The manipulation leads to privilege escalation. It is possible to launch the attack remotely.
